                Iantumalius Blato<lb break="no" n="2"/>nis <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>ues</ex></expan> alae I <expan><abbr>Itur</abbr><ex>aeorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>XXX s<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>tip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan></supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex cert="low"/>V</expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/><expan><abbr>ZO</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan><supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Fries mit zwei Pferden, Pferdeführer und Soldat; darüber zwei männliche Büsten.</p>
